responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "3B4539F44ABF19CDF918159BE5429618", "That\'s a relief. As soon as we drive out the goblins, bums and muggers creep into the cracks they leave behind. It\'s all that we can do to keep the rabble around here down and our pilgrims safe! Get out there and make sure no-one untoward is skulking about will you? Once that\'s done we can take on the real business.")
